<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 12:16:25 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列国防军告诉家长，黎巴嫩边境 75% 的以色列军队观察员已从前线撤离</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/75-of-israeli-army-spotters-on-lebanese-border-moved-from-frontline-idf-tells-parents/00000191-bca1-dd1b-a7db-bfff62bc0000</link><description>以色列国防军观察员的父母向以色列高等法院请愿，回应驻黎巴嫩边境观察员的投诉，称他们的基地在真主党袭击中避难所不足，并且担心类似于哈马斯 10 月 7 日对纳哈尔奥兹军事哨所实施的袭击</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 11:53:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/75-of-israeli-army-spotters-on-lebanese-border-moved-from-frontline-idf-tells-parents/00000191-bca1-dd1b-a7db-bfff62bc0000</guid></item><item><title>“他脱下裤子并说‘过来看看’：巴勒斯坦希伯伦女性居民报告遭到以色列士兵的骚扰</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/female-palestinian-hebron-residents-claim-harassment-by-israeli-soldiers/00000191-bc9e-d9c6-a997-bebe2ae40000</link><description>一名来自约旦河西岸城市希伯伦的妇女最近报告称遭到一名以色列士兵的骚扰。其他女性表示这不是一起孤立事件，并讲述了辱骂和未经授权搜查手机的情况</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 11:42:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/female-palestinian-hebron-residents-claim-harassment-by-israeli-soldiers/00000191-bc9e-d9c6-a997-bebe2ae40000</guid></item><item><title>纽约时报托马斯·弗里德曼表示，内塔尼亚胡升级加沙战争以帮助特朗普赢得选举</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/netanyahu-escalating-gaza-war-to-help-trump-win-elections-nyts-thomas-friedman-says/00000191-bc6b-dd1b-a7db-bfffdf070000</link><description>《纽约时报》专栏作家托马斯·弗里德曼认为，内塔尼亚胡在加沙协议谈判期间做出的决定是为了在即将到来的选举中强化特朗普，他认为特朗普将在政治上帮助他</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 10:48:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/netanyahu-escalating-gaza-war-to-help-trump-win-elections-nyts-thomas-friedman-says/00000191-bc6b-dd1b-a7db-bfffdf070000</guid></item><item><title>联盟消息来源：内塔尼亚胡几周前决定反对人质交易，并发现费城是一个有效的旋转</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/coalition-source-netanyahu-decided-against-hostage-deal-weeks-ago-philadelphi-is-a-spin/00000191-bc3a-dc3b-a7df-ff7a0ab60000</link><description>就像一个真正的独裁者一样，总理正在拿人质的生命开玩笑。部长和议员们仍然袖手旁观，不采取任何行动来拯救人质，其中一些人发表了强烈声明支持达成协议</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 10:07:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/coalition-source-netanyahu-decided-against-hostage-deal-weeks-ago-philadelphi-is-a-spin/00000191-bc3a-dc3b-a7df-ff7a0ab60000</guid></item><item><title>在共和党与犹太人的会议上，共和党宣布自己是美国唯一亲以色列的政党</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-09-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/at-republican-jewish-confab-gop-set-to-proclaim-itself-americas-only-pro-israel-party/00000191-b8ca-de3d-abb7-feeb37410000</link><description>本周在拉斯维加斯举行的共和党犹太联盟年度聚会上，共和党人可能会支持以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的信息，即优先考虑对哈马斯的“全面胜利”，并希望在 11 月获得自己的胜利</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 09:09:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-09-04/ty-article-magazine/.premium/at-republican-jewish-confab-gop-set-to-proclaim-itself-americas-only-pro-israel-party/00000191-b8ca-de3d-abb7-feeb37410000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方过去两天拒绝释放50多名被拘留的抗议者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-refuse-to-release-over-50-detained-protesters-over-past-two-days/00000191-bbdd-d13c-a39b-bfdd5d3a0000</link><description>在几乎所有案件中，法院都拒绝了警方延长抗议者拘留期限的请求。在某些案件中，法官批评警方没有提供针对被捕者的证据，或者提供的证据特别少</description><pubDate>Wed, 04 Sep 2024 09:02:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-04/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-re