aviv-calling-for-a-hostage-release-deal/00000191-b900-d13c-a39b-bf8d09ff0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第333天：消息人士告诉CNN，内塔尼亚胡“鱼雷”破坏了停战谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-333-netanyahu-torpedoed-truce-talks-source-tells-cnn/00000191-b88e-d13c-a39b-be8fdaa80001</link><description>消息人士告诉美国有线电视新闻网，内塔尼亚胡宣布以色列永远不会离开费城走廊，从而“破坏”了恢复人质释放谈判的努力。 10 月 7 日，战争可能导致国际刑事法院对内塔尼亚胡、国防部长加兰特发出逮捕令 ■ 这是战争开始 333 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 17:20:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-333-netanyahu-torpedoed-truce-talks-source-tells-cnn/00000191-b88e-d13c-a39b-be8fdaa80001</guid></item><item><title>以色列财政部长斯莫特里奇提议对2025年预算采取严格的财务措施</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/israeli-finance-minister-smotrich-proposes-strict-financial-measures-for-2025-budget/00000191-b805-d13c-a39b-be8d59150000</link><description>这位极右翼部长说，我们正处于战争之中，但我们将在经济战线上共同获胜。拟议的措施包括冻结所得税等级、冻结公共部门工资、冻结最低工资以及取消游客增值税豁免。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 15:12:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/israeli-finance-minister-smotrich-proposes-strict-financial-measures-for-2025-budget/00000191-b805-d13c-a39b-be8d59150000</guid></item><item><title>两名西岸定居者因袭击阿拉伯以色列妇女而被起诉；一名被指控犯有恐怖罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/two-west-bank-settlers-indicted-for-assaulting-arab-israeli-women-one-charged-with-terror/00000191-b7a5-dffe-abf9-bfffe8200000</link><description>来自约旦河西岸定居点的两名男子被指控犯有出于种族动机的罪行，其中一名男子在袭击了来自贝都因市拉哈特的四名妇女和一名幼儿后，还被指控犯有恐怖主义罪</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 14:45:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/two-west-bank-settlers-indicted-for-assaulting-arab-israeli-women-one-charged-with-terror/00000191-b7a5-dffe-abf9-bfffe8200000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡发表了一番激动人心、夸夸其谈的演讲，终结了人质协议的希望</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/with-a-chest-thumping-bombastic-speech-netanyahu-ends-hope-for-a-hostage-deal/00000191-b79b-dd1b-a7db-b7dfa8860000</link><description>在首次向人质家属请求宽恕后，以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡又回到了自己的本性：连续撒谎，无视令人不快的事实，并承诺以牺牲协议为代价留在费城路线上。</description><pubDate>Tue, 03 Sep 2024 14:08:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-03/ty-article/.premium/with-a-chest-thumping-bombastic-speech-netanyahu-ends-hope-for-a-hostage-deal/00000191-b79b-dd1b-a7db-b7dfa8860000</guid></item></channel></rss>